# Thunderstorm rules index

Non-negotiable principles are in [project-for-any-project.mdc](project-for-any-project.mdc) (lighthouse). This file is the **single routing table** to all thunderstorm rules.

Read [vocabulary](_thunderstorm/.rules/vocabulary.mdc) first for the core mental model. Then use the table below to find the right rule by intent.

Paths are relative to the project root (monorepo root).

